# Requirements

PureUserAdmin requires :
  
  * A http server
  * PHP5 or PHP7, with PDO support (mysql, pgsql, sqlite etc)
  * MySQL/PostgreSQL daemon.
    * PureFTPd with mysql/postgresql auth config
	* A webbrowser

# Installation.

  * Unpack it somewhere ...
  * Configure Apache to read from the public/ directory.
  * If there is no vendor/ directory get Composer (https://getcomposer.org) and run ```composer install ```
  * Edit config.php to reflect your system.

